      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Painters & Painting Contractors
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Homeowners hiring a painter are wary of fly-by-night contractors who do shoddy work, leave a mess, or disappear mid-job. Customer testimonials that address those exact fears — quality, cleanliness, reliability, and fair pricing — win you more estimates than any ad.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What painting customers actually worry about</h2>
      <p>They're not buying a commodity — they're letting strangers into their home with paint and ladders. Their fears: cutting corners on prep, sloppy edges, drips on the floor, price changing after the job starts, not showing up when promised. A testimonial that says "they showed up on time every day, protected our floors and furniture, and the trim lines are perfect" is a direct answer to every objection.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Painting testimonials that win more bids</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Cleanliness:</strong> "They left my house cleaner than when they arrived. I was shocked."</li>
        <li><strong>Quality detail work:</strong> "The trim is perfect. Straight lines everywhere — obvious they take pride in their craft."</li>
        <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> "Showed up when they said they would, every single day. Finished a day early."</li>
        <li><strong>Fair pricing:</strong> "Quote was exactly what I paid. No surprise charges at the end."</li>
        <li><strong>Repeat customer:</strong> "Used them for the exterior last year and just booked them for the interior. Already recommended them to three neighbors."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Build your review base after every job</h2>
      <p>Send your SocialProof collection link via text on the final day of the job — while the customer is standing in their freshly painted space and feeling great about it. The response rate is dramatically higher right after job completion than days later. Display your testimonials on your estimate request page to pre-qualify high-intent leads.</p>

